dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: Attention, everyone! Reinforcements have arrived!!
W-Who are those people?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: For sure, who could these be, Shrenne~? Made new friends other than me?

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: They're Fixers from Rosespanner Workshop, the ones we're working with for the current project. They've visited here several times already, you really should be familiar by now.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Pleasure to meet you. I'm Niko, representative of Rosespanner Workshop.
The enemies' faces clouded over at the unexpected arrival of reinforcements.

dataList.title: Terrorist Organization?
dataList.content: Boring. Let's head back.

dataList.title: Terrorist Organization?
dataList.content: What?

dataList.title: Terrorist Organization?
dataList.content: Sure... We'll leave.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: Would you look at that, our "aura" has made them flee out of terror... Huhu...

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Thanks, Shrenne. This made me seriously consider the possibility that your department might be picked as the best next year for the first time.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: Shame about your precious trophies being destroyed, huh?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Ms. Shrenne, pardon me for suspecting, but you did not perchance wait until the trophies were broken before bringing reinforcements, did you?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: I don't mind losing them.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: As long as the photo is fine.
The damage they left is pretty severe now that I'm seeing it firsthand...
It could've gotten all the researchers killed if things went wrong.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Indeed, which is why we must eliminate them and reclaim the facility they've occupied as soon as possible.
Why, then, does K Corp... not provide assistance?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Mmm... Clearly, it's because they don't want the general public to know that such a thing happened in the Nest, don't you think?
While I may concede on that matter as innocent feathers were involved, this concerns researchers and a laboratory directly affiliated with the Wing...

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: It's evidence that they want it to remain discrete that much, don't you think?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Anyway, I ought to bring a generous supply of regeneration ampules for you all to use. Now should be a good time to depart, right?
We aren't going on a picnic, Dongrang... You gonna be okay?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: No problem, seeing you in battle made me all the more reassured about accompanying you.
Just so you know... the technology our manager Dante uses is on a different level compared to K Corp's ampules; rather than regenerate, it restores.
Therefore, observing it won't provide much insight that can be applied to K Corp's Singularity or regeneration ampules.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Restoration, not healing, huh...
No way~ Is he trying to copy Dante's ability like what that shady Bodhisattva Chicken guy tried with his rival?!

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: I wouldn't do such a thing. I'm not the kind of person to cram down food that I know I can't digest.
It has to be common practice for someone like you to send capable underlings to do the fighting for you, and yet you insist on being on the front. Are you that hungry for a medal?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: No, it's that I left...

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: A number of things I couldn't take with me in time.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Like the photo commemorating my third consecutive year of winning the excellence award, the plaque of appreciation from K Corp, the photo taken to celebrate my lab's expansion, and... what else was there, Samjo?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: ...Classified documents concerning the research, sir...
...So it's more that you wanted to gain back the medals you had.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Oh right, that too.
You really did just barely manage to escape there, huh...

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: I guarantee you, that nerd Dongrang has never swung a fist in his life. He's too carefree. At least bring some Fixers like me.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Is your department going as well, Ms. Shrenne?

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: I don't see how you could benefit from the success of this operation.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: ...Three of my coworkers died in their last attack.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: I've lost too much to care about interests and benefits.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Ms. Shrenne...

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: In that case, will I be correct to assume that the payment for the Fixers will be handled by your department--

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: Ugh... You just can't stop being such an irritating bunch...

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: The Lobotomy Corp. branch we must reclaim isn't too far from here.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: Let's head there together.

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: I was hoping I could get a ride on your bus... What a shame.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: I'll secure you an opportunity next time. Let's get moving for now.
Huh? Who do you think you are to decide that...?!

dataList.place: Way to Lobotomy Corp. Branch in Nest K
dataList.content: This mission felt particularly tumultuous.
And then, you see~ I bet the chips and declared like this:
"All~ in."
Haah... I wanna stop hearing it... It's giving me nausea.

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: There's nothing like headshake poker at J Corp's casinos. Those people who sit at the slot machines all day long, they're all morons.
What, you mean there's something up with the machines?

dataList.title: Rosespanner Workshop
dataList.content: This is something I haven't told anyone else. You see...
Hold on, you gotta explain in more detail...
<Things are lively this time around.>
D.L.I.
"She says she doesn't like it," whispered Sinclair.
I whispered back to him saying "I know".
